  "3183410": {
    "name": "The Bench",
    "steam_appid": 3183410,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183410/extras/1ddaabc8fd19ce65521cf48c8b50cc3b.avif?t=1769520714\" width=1024 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是否曾经想过，做一个坐在公园长椅上的老人是什么感觉？他整天都在做什么？手里拿着报纸，陷入沉思，看着时间一点点流逝……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手握拐杖，带着无尽的面包（还有许多舒适的长椅），你将探索一个充满谜题、隐藏物品、当然还有——鸽子的多彩世界！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183410/extras/b26703ecf9f1d5a74796e9461c0f7c26.poster.avif?t=1769520714\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183410/extras/b26703ecf9f1d5a74796e9461c0f7c26.webm?t=1769520714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183410/extras/b26703ecf9f1d5a74796e9461c0f7c26.mp4?t=1769520714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在旅途中，你将带领一群越来越大的可爱鸽子队伍，它们可以完全自定义，并会服从你的每一个指令：让它们偷取有用的物品、帮你解谜，或只是陪你一起钓鱼、涂鸦、打个盹。 在 <i>The Bench</i> 中，鸽子是你最好的朋友。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183410/extras/f33e99e100058d922e0581deb20d9f52.poster.avif?t=1769520714\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183410/extras/f33e99e100058d922e0581deb20d9f52.webm?t=1769520714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183410/extras/f33e99e100058d922e0581deb20d9f52.mp4?t=1769520714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对公园的游客和维修工开一些无伤大雅的玩笑：打断野餐、搅乱派对、把路人扔进水里——你可以按照自己的方式与世界互动！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183410/extras/2108a53d6a007f431c8398ceb7ee79e4.poster.avif?t=1769520714\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183410/extras/2108a53d6a007f431c8398ceb7ee79e4.webm?t=1769520714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183410/extras/2108a53d6a007f431c8398ceb7ee79e4.mp4?t=1769520714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索设计精美、色彩鲜艳的地图，每张都有独特的风格。投入到各种有趣的小游戏中：解谜、在笔记本上画画、下棋、玩滚球、踢足球或去钓鱼。 总有事情能让你的大脑保持清醒，让你不会打瞌睡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183410/extras/0c2e8759bfad27c11fea763b69b244ee.poster.avif?t=1769520714\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183410/extras/0c2e8759bfad27c11fea763b69b244ee.webm?t=1769520714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3183410/extras/0c2e8759bfad27c11fea763b69b244ee.mp4?t=1769520714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对于喜欢解谜、找物和冒险游戏的玩家来说，<i>The Bench</i> 是放松与挑战的完美结合，带着一丝温暖的幽默。<br>游戏还包含一系列独特的 Twitch 集成功能，等待你去发现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
